 //
 // Multi-Token Prediction (MTP / NextN) draft
 //
-// This is a thin public-API entry point that validates inputs and delegates
-// to the model's MTP head graph builder (see llm_build_qwen3next::build_mtp_head).
+// Builds a synthetic single-token ubatch, dispatches it through the qwen3next
+// MTP graph (LLM_GRAPH_TYPE_MTP), and reads back vocab logits. Repeated K
+// times to produce K draft tokens via greedy argmax. The graph builder lives
